data.description: Unprecedented Value in Monck's Corner! 5BR/3BTH with guest suite on main floor! Nicely appointed kitchen features marble countertops, stainless appliances and painted maple cabinetry. All overlooking spacious great room! Plan highlights include walk in butler's pantry (coffee station? wine bar?), formal dining, and first floor guest room w/ full bath! Second Floor Owner's Suite with large walk in closet plus en suite! Spacious secondary bedrooms plus game room for additional entertaining space or play room!
